Description:DmC - this new series Devil May Cry, in which the protagonist Dante became more like the protagonist of "Twilight", although pistols, sword and cloak were gone nowhere. For the development of DmC Devil May Cry meets British team Ninja Theory - the creators Enslaved and Heavenly Sword. Changing the developer has not passed for the world Devil May Cry unnoticed - the game became more realistic, dark and cinematic.
